Description

Winning a hackathon to upgrade my mouse…
35Likes
687Views
Oct 32025
#ai #robotics #tech #programming #hackathon #coding Someone roasted me in my last video for building a whole robot but still using a $15 mouse. So naturally, I entered my very first hackathon to win a better one. The theme? AI + Education. The time limit? 6 hours. My friends and I decided to build a Chrome extension for Canvas with: ✅ An AI that ranks tasks by importance 💬 A chatbot that answers assignment questions (sometimes by… vibes) I was in charge of the chatbot, and let’s just say there was a lot of vibecoding with Cursor AI, an unhealthy amount of Celsius, and pure chaos until the very last 30 minutes. Somehow, everything came together just in time for demo day — and against all odds, we actually took 2nd place, winning new keyboards and $300 of AI credits. I might still have the cheap mouse, but at least now I can type faster. 10/10 hackathon — would recommend, especially for the free food. …...more
